Ivan Sergei https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ivan_Sergei 0 Ivan Sergei (; born May 7, 1971) is an American actor known for his work in television. His best known roles are Dr. Peter Winslow in Crossing Jordan and Henry Mitchell in Charmed. Ivan_Sergei ( ; born May_7 , 1971 ) is an_American_actor known for his_work in television .
